    <h2 style="color:red"> Limitations of ChatGPT <!-- <span class="chapterTitle"> "Down the Rabbit Hole" </span> --> </h2> 

        

        <p style="line-height: 3;">
            ChatGPT may write responses that sound like they are correct, but are incorrect. </br>
            It may answer some questions differently or not at all even if both questions logically are the same, just worded differently </br>
            Sometimes it will give wordy responses and overuse some phrases, like how it's a language model trained by OpenAI. </br>
            When reponding to ambiguous questions, the model tries to guess what the question is, instead of clarifying it. </br>
            The model responds to inappropriate requests and show bad behavior. 
        </p>

