            reponses to very complex questions. It is able to respond incredibly quickly, faster than any human could respond </br>
            It is always running 24/7, except crashes though that doesn't count. It can talk to multiple users at once, giving </br>
            good responses regardless of the amount of people using it. This is something humans cannot do, one person cannot talk to </br>
            thousands of people at once and give good responses to all of them. ChatGPT knows a lot of topics and has a large knowledge base </br>
